      "description": "Looking for a practical, affordable ride that gets you where you need to go? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great option for everyday commuting and errands. You'll find some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with age, but nothing that gets in the way of dependable transportation. If you're after a no-fuss, budget-friendly vehicle that delivers solid value, this one deserves a look!",
