    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and it truly represents the best you'll find on the market today. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, vibrant gloss with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and every panel aligns perfectly. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear: the upholstery is pristine, all surfaces are clean and unmarked, and every electronic and mechanical feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and running smoothly, with full service history available. This is a turn-key, move-in-ready vehicle for the buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
