    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Dependable & Ready for the Road \u2013 A True Good-Condition Gem! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis vehicle has been well cared for and it truly shows! It runs smoothly, handles everyday driving with confidence, and has been maintained with attention to detail. You'll notice the care that's gone into keeping it in good shape \u2014 this isn't a perfect car, but it's a genuinely reliable one that won't let you down. Whether it's your daily commute, weekend errands, or a road trip, this ride is up to the task. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself \u2014 good condition, honest price, no surprises! \ud83d\ude4c",
