    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find Alert! \ud83c\udf1f This stunning vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! From bumper to bumper, inside and out, this car looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint gleams, the interior is spotless, all systems run flawlessly, and every detail has been meticulously maintained. Whether you're a car enthusiast looking for something truly special or simply a buyer who refuses to settle for less than the best, this is the one you've been waiting for. Opportunities like this don't come around often \u2014 don't let it slip away!",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should enter with clear, realistic expectations. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas of paint damage or rust that are visually apparent. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require substantial repairs before it can be considered fully reliable \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or in need of parts. It may still start and move under its own power, but it should not be assumed to be road-ready without a thorough inspection and repair investment. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the car's current state honestly.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a full, honest picture before you decide. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents or structural concerns to report. The interior is clean and well-kept, with modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, stains, or significant damage. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems including brakes, suspension, and cooling are in good working order. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring any immediate major repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
